name: Pool (COMPUTE! Publications)
overview: Pool is a simple pool/billiards game for 1 or 2 players. It was developed by Kevin Mykytyn. It was published in the following: - COMPUTE!'s Gazette 1985/04 (Issue #22) (original release) - Best of COMPUTE! & Gazette - Super VIC & C64 A2-N07 (July/August 1985) (Italian magazine)
